Total to Expand Chemicals Business, Cornelis Tells Handelsblatt

-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 
2011-11-29T05:59:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-29/total-to-expand-chemicals-business-cornelis-tells-handelsblatt.html
Total SA (FP)  plans to invest about 2
billion euros ($2.7 billion) in its chemical divisions over the
next few years and expand in  Asia ,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing
Deputy Chief Executive Officer Francois Cornelis.  The Paris-based company plans to invest about one billion
euros each in its petrochemical and specialty chemicals
divisions, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
 snicola2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  